            "a2": "Click \"Add Group\" on the home page. Enter the group name and select students who don't have a group yet.",
            "q3": "How does attendance work?",
            "a3": "Click \"Mark Attendance\" to record individual or group lessons. Fees are automatically added to student balances.",
            "q4": "How to collect payment?",
            "a4": "Go to student details. Enter amount and press \"Add\". The amount is deducted from balance.",
            "q5": "How to send WhatsApp message?",
            "a5": "In student details, click \"Share via WhatsApp\". This generates a pre-filled WhatsApp message with balance and lesson info.",
            "q6": "How to change theme color?",
            "a6": "Go to \"Profile\" tab. Select a color in \"Brand Color\" and press \"Save\".",
            "q7": "How to backup data?",
            "a7": "In \"Profile\", press \"Export Data\". Save the file. Use \"Import Data\" to load it back."
